OL,4,CRuth Madeley: Actress says taxi driver
OL,5,Ctook her wheelchair away
OL,6, Actress Ruth Madeley has told of how a
OL,7, taxi driver took her wheelchair away
OL,8, following an argument outside London's
OL,9, Euston station last month.
OL,11,FThe Bafta nominee said the driver told
OL,12,Fher it was "too difficult" to drop her
OL,13,Fat an accessible entrance and it wasn't
OL,14,Fhis problem if she couldn't use stairs.
OL,16,FAfter a dispute over payment, she said
OL,17,Fhe then took her wheelchair, put it in
OL,18,Fhis boot and refused to give it back.
OL,20,FTransport for London has apologised for
OL,21,Fthe "utterly appalling" incident.
